@JJMMFFF I dunno... I really felt the story was presented very well. It gave you a sense of awkwardness within each scene that gave it much more realistic feel. And  each character went through their own transformation.
I also found myself responding to them  and expecting a reply. I really felt like I was part of the story. Normally  I need a custom character for that...
It  may not have been the best writing but it was definitely the best delivery I've ever seen.
